    "The selected sentiment classification test sets have 2 options: negative and positive.",
    "The number of words for reading comprehension refers to the lengths of the contexts.",
    "It is seen that the test sets considered have varying lengths from 200 to 700 words and 75 to 230 words for reading comprehension and sentiment classification tasks respectively.",
